### Create a new category
POST http://localhost:4000/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "study",
    "color": "#4287f5",
    "user_id": 1
}

### Get category by id
GET http://localhost:4000/v1/categories/6

### Patch category by id
PATCH http://localhost:4000/v1/categories/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "work"
}

